<h2>How Do I Join?</h2>
Applications are accepted throughout the year with names placed on a Wait List.  Beginning in January, as slots are available, the League Secretary begins contacting Wait List ladies inviting them to join. (We've generally brought in approx 25 ladies each year.) Membership is closed each year by the end of April.
